flowchart TD
  A([Start]) --> B[POST /v1/quests/:questId/claim]
  B --> C[Resolve player context]
  C --> D[Load quest progress]
  D --> E{Completed and not claimed?}
  E -->|No| X[Return cannot claim]
  E -->|Yes| F[Compute reward]
  F --> G[Apply reward to player state]
  G --> H[Insert reward transaction]
  H --> I[Mark quest as claimed]
  I --> J[Return updated quest + reward]
  X --> Z([End])
  J --> Z
